Resource Profile: Claims

Official URL: https://shr.tiberbuapps.com/fhir/StructureDefinition/ClaimProfile Version: 0.1.0
Active as of 2024-08-23 Computable Name: ClaimProfile

Standardise the format of electronic claims / pre-authorizations / pre-determinations.

This profile constrains the representation of a Kenyan electronic claim.

Usage:

  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Claim/ClaimProfileExample

: contained.meta.security.empty()

: text.`div`.exists()
